{"tid":2024363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧發表聲明祝賀「總統」蔡英文連任  指台灣抗疫表現值得參考","createTime":"2020-05-19T14:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T23:57:00.000Z","uid":2054,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff135e0fa152d6e35470dcdfd59b09886a5e212","tid":2024363,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:29:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527122-20200519.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527122-20200519.htm&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7mINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=91f708e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527122-20200519.htm&h=f15abe6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527122-20200519.htm</a><br />\n2020-05-19 HKT 22:24<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧發表聲明，祝賀蔡英文。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧以「總統」 稱呼蔡英文，指出蔡英文以顯著票數差距成功連任，顯示她贏得台灣民眾的尊敬、欽佩及信任，而她帶領民主的勇氣與願景，亦鼓舞了地區及世界。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧又說，台灣應對新型冠狀病毒疫情的表現，值得參考。<br />\n<br />\n在台灣，成功連任的蔡英文總統，明天發表就職演說。發言人說，演說內容包括產業發展、社會安定、台灣安全、及民主深化四大方向。"},{"pid":"09a4891a52d040bc6ff2720b33d134ff40e2b11d","tid":2024363,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"問心 大家想唔想香港獨立建國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"69db5d2f4829b218169c9cd5c464de51bd9b8502","tid":2024363,"uid":120480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T23:57:00.000Z","msg":"無人理？"}]}